Nice work!

Some tips though ;), only constructive and it’s only if you want it to be runable.

Rename Applet -> AppletSub or make the superclass of it java.applet.Applet and do not import it! Otherwise you get compile error
Same for Canvas
There is a statement Character.Type rename it to java.lang.Character.Type (else error with Character class)
There are 3 int[] is = (new {shorts}); change to int[]
Some errors because of the class Socket and the java.net.Socket
Also errors with Image and java.awt.Image
